Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.16,0:00:28.67,Consolas,,0,0,0,,I'll pretend I don't notice!
Comment: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:09.23,Consolas,,0,0,0,,没味道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:09.23,Consolas,,0,0,0,,There's no taste.
