Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:10.99,Consolas,,0,0,0,,Was it completely devoured?
Comment: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:12.95,Consolas,,0,0,0,,这就是梦魔的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:12.95,Consolas,,0,0,0,,So this is the power of Nightmare.
